first thing we want to do is import our data. Doing that is quite simple. 
First get your working directory use the code -> getwd() this will going to give your working directory
Then go ahead and find your directory in your computers files or mac's finder 
Put your table in that working directory, preferably in your project section.
Most Absorbance data comes in excel so in this tutorial excel will be used.
Now you should see your excell under your files section in Rstudios 
Click on it and say import, if you dont have headers remove the thick in "names as first row"
You should see your data in your enviorment.
